snippet.title: Best VGM 1213 - Double Dragon Neon - City Streets 2 (Mango Tango - Neon Jungle)
snippet.description:
Get the album @ http://virt.bandcamp.com/album/double-dragon-neon

See also:
Best VGM 1371 - http://youtu.be/8x1E_1TY8ig

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
Double Dragon Neon (2012)
City Streets 2 ~ Mango Tango - Neon Jungle
Jake Kaufman
